urdu transliteration text:
Babajaan Me Rida Mangti Rehgayi, Baamo Dar Saj Gaye, Jiteji Margayi,Halqaye Shaam Me, Nam Sunkar MeraMargaya NaatawanFATHER I KEPT ASKING FOR VEIL,I WAS BROKEN SEEING ALL THE DECORATED BUILDINGS,IMAM SAJJAD WAS GRIEF STRICKEN WHEN HEARD BY NAME IN SHAAM
@HujjatELC
Ay Mere Babajaan- OH MY DEAREST FATHER

Shaam Ashur Se, Shamo Kufa Talak, Maine Manga Nahi Hai Kharaje Fadak,Meri Chadar Se Hai, Meri Maa Ka SukunSunle Zalim JahaanFROM THE NIGHT OF ASHURA, TO SHAM AND KUFA
@HujjatELC
Ay Mere Babajaan- OH MY DEAREST FATHER

Ruk Na Paya Mere Bawafa Ka Wo Sar, Noke Neza Se Aane Laga Khaak Par,Behn Ko Darbadar, Dekhkar Nange SarSeh Na Paya JawaanTHE HEAD OF ABBAS FELL TO THE GROUND FROM THE SPEAR,AFTER SEEING HIS SISTER WITHOUT A VEIL EVERYWHERE,ABBAS COULDN’T BEAR THE SCENES
@HujjatELC
Ay Mere Babajaan- OH MY DEAREST FATHER
